<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>The Infinite Web Page</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: lightyellow;
            color: darkblue;
        }
        .infinite {
            font-size: 2em;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .nested-div {
            margin: 50px;
            padding: 30px;
            border: 5px solid #000;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>The Biggest Web Page That Never Ends</h1>
    <p>Welcome to the infinite web page, where the content never ends and loops forever in your mind!</p>

    <div class="infinite">
        <h2>This is an infinitely nested div!</h2>
        <div class="nested-div">
            <div class="nested-div">
                <div class="nested-div">
                    <div class="nested-div">
                        <div class="nested-div">
                            <div class="nested-div">
                                <!-- You can repeat this an absurd number of times -->
                                <p>Are you still here?</p>
                                <p>Yep, it keeps going!</p>
                                <p>And going... And going...</p>
                                <p>You're in too deep now, there's no turning back!</p>
                                <p>Want a break? Scroll back up... Oh wait, you can't!</p>
                                <p>And yet, there's more!</p>
                                <p>Does this page have an end? No!</p>
                                <p>Keep going...</p>
                                <p>How many divs deep are we?</p>
                                <p>Guess we'll never know!</p>
                                <!-- More content -->
                                <h3>Endless Lists!</h3>
                                <ul>
                                    <li>This list is never ending</li>
                                    <li>It's eternal</li>
                                    <li>Forever</li>
                                    <li>Looping...</li>
                                    <li>And repeating!</li>
                                    <li>Infinity is just around the corner</li>
                                    <li>Or is it?</li>
                                    <li>You have reached div-ception!</li>
                                </ul>

                                <h3>The Infinite Table</h3>
                                <table border="1">
                                    <tr><th>Row</th><th>Column</th></tr>
                                    <tr><td>1</td><td>1</td></tr>
                                    <tr><td>2</td><td>2</td></tr>
                                    <tr><td>3</td><td>3</td></tr>
                                    <tr><td>∞</td><td>∞</td></tr>
                                    <tr><td>Infinity</td><td>Infinity</td></tr>
                                </table>

                                <h3>Inception of Divs!</h3>
                                <div class="nested-div">
                                    <div class="nested-div">
                                        <div class="nested-div">
                                            <!-- Another level of nested insanity -->
                                            <p>This div is inside a div inside a div inside a div...</p>
                                            <p>And there's more... Keep scrolling!</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <!-- The infinite scrolling -->
                                <div style="height:1000px;">Keep scrolling down...</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <p>End of the endless web page? Just kidding. There's no end!</p>

    <!-- Infinite scrolling text -->
    <marquee behavior="scroll" direction="left" scrollamount="10">You can never escape this page. It loops forever. You are stuck here. Forever...</marquee>

</body>
</html>
